<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-21-0359 </DOCNO><TEXT>The status is summarized of three bills before the 100th Congress relatedto geothermal energy. The bills are the Geothermal Energy Control Actof 1987 (H.R. 235), the Federal Lands Receipts Clarification Act (H.R.1662), and the Geothermal Steam Act Amendments of 1987 (S. 1006). Abstractsof the bills and legislative actions on each are given.</TEXT></DOC>